public class ServerObjectImpl
extends ServerObjectPOA

Author:
Quynh Nguyen This is the implementation of the ServerObject interface, which serves as a callback when the JacORB is registered with a TAO ImR. It allows the TAO ImR to ping a JacORB server and shutdown the server when needed.
